Package gov.usgs.earthquake.shakemap

Class ShakeMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.earthquake.product.Product
      • gov.usgs.earthquake.shakemap.ShakeMap
  • public class ShakeMap
extends Product
    ShakeMap class for ShakeMap products specifically. This subclass of Product provides access to additional ShakeMap-specific attributes and loads these attributes, as well as additional Product attributes from ShakeMap source XML files.
